94
00:05:24,789 --> 00:05:25,978
- Bring it on.
- Bring it on.

95
00:05:25,978 --> 00:05:27,548
- Bring it on.
- Come on. Throw the first fist.

96
00:05:27,548 --> 00:05:29,188
- Bring it on.
- Bring it on. Throw the first fist.

