108
00:06:36,107 --> 00:06:36,802
What do you want to do?

109
00:06:38,088 --> 00:06:39,261
Let’s call a truce.

110
00:06:45,754 --> 00:06:49,411
Many rival gang members become friends 
when they are sent to a detention center.

111
00:06:51,522 --> 00:06:52,542
You and I.

112
00:06:55,939 --> 00:06:57,183
We can be something

113
